{"tid":2275634,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"12港人家屬要求公開官派律師資料被拒","createTime":"2020-11-07T10:06:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T12:40:45.000Z","uid":310867,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ea939c62662083fe1141ef0ed431311c42f00e80","tid":2275634,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T10:06:28.000Z","msg":"十二名港人被內地拘留，家屬要求公開官派律師的資料被拒。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，有家屬收到深圳市公安局鹽田分局的回覆指出，根據政府信息公開條例規定，政府信息是指行政機關在履行行政管理職能過程中製作或獲取，以一定形式記錄及保存的信息，家屬申請公開刑事案件信息，並非政府信息，因此申請並不適用。<br />\n<br />\n鹽田分局表示，家屬如有不服，可以在60日內向深圳市公安局或鹽田區政府申請行政復議，或者在6個月內依法向鹽田區人民法院提出行政訴訟。<br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\nRTHK"},{"pid":"e59af24344263c1eacbfd92a3c9ba1cbdb4d357a","tid":2275634,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T10:08:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558857-20201107.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558857-20201107.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=J7URIij%2BjV7QbFiEH5rjuICLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=f1269238\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558857-20201107.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e96cc8b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558857-20201107.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"7121d2c4b447a938c6f53506eb45dd6667975622","tid":2275634,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T10:10:08.000Z","msg":"#Save12"},{"pid":"ed1be8cf0ef61807fd75a439201a41a72579daec","tid":2275634,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T10:12:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8c79088b06d678924f7b190e176e47d1ce0b0242","tid":2275634,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T10:13:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\